item.title: CVE-2023-27530|2023-12-08T22:06:17.311008 -- n%2Fa -- https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Frack%2Frack
item.description: A DoS vulnerability exists in Rack <v3.0.4.2, <v2.2.6.3, <v2.1.4.3 and <v2.0.9.3 within in the Multipart MIME parsing code in which could allow an attacker to craft requests that can be abuse to cause multipart parsing to take longer than expected.
